## Test 5: Comments
## Tests single-line comment handling

## Empty comment (just ##)
##

## Comment with numbers
## 12345 67890

## Comment with punctuators
## ( ) { } [ ] , ; :

## Comment with operators
## ++ -- + - * /

## Comment with booleans and identifiers
## true false Count Variable_name

## Inline comments after valid tokens
42 ## inline after integer
+100 ## inline after signed integer
3.14 ## inline after float
true ## inline after boolean
false ## inline after boolean
Count ## inline after identifier
++ ## inline after increment
( ## inline after punctuator

## Comment at end of file with no newline
## this is the last line